story.text: Soooo much snow. Terrible driving conditions. Didn't make it into Billings, even though I intended to.

I used to love Christmas. Now I am a bit of a Grinch. I hope to find myself somewhere in the middle. Neither loving nor hating Christmas - just observing the spirit and energy of the season without judgement.
